Snort (IDS mode)

# Installation

$ ./setup.sh

$ sudo vi /etc/sudoers  
	Add the following line at the end of the file
	[YourID] ALL=NOPASSWD:ALL

$ sudo vi /etc/network/interfaces
	auto eth1
	iface eth1 inet manual

$ sudo reboot  

# Execution

./start.sh (normal mode)
./start.sh b (daemon mode)
./stop.sh

# Information

Here, Snort uses the latest community rules for intrusion detection
